  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, the cricket final is in three days — what snacks will you have at 7:00 PM? I'm a tea person, but you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I'll have some samosas and chai. It's a tradition during big matches. How about you? Any specific snacks you like?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Samosas and chai — classic! I like to have tea and biscuits during matches. What’s your favorite team in the final?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "My team is Mumbai Indians, obviously! They've been doing really well this season. I don't know about you, but I get so nervous when the game is close. Do you follow it closely?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Mumbai Indians are a strong team — good choice! I watch the game when I have time. Close matches are exciting. Do you have a favorite player?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Sachin Tendulkar is my favorite, of course. He's a legend. I also like Virat Kohli a lot. They both play with so much heart. Do you follow any players?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Sachin and Virat — great picks! I admire their dedication. Do you watch every match or only the big ones?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I try to watch most matches if I can, but sometimes work gets in the way. The final is definitely a must-watch. By the way, are you watching the practice games too? I've been a bit busy this week. Acha, I should probably get some rest before the big day."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re doing great — work can be tough. Rest well, the final is important. I’ll watch the final, no worries. Tell me, what time do you sleep usually?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I usually sleep around 11 or 12, but lately, it's been more like 1 or 2. I have trouble winding down, especially with the final coming up. Umm, I think I'll try to go to bed earlier tonight. Thanks for asking."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds tough — late nights are hard. Winding down can be tricky. What helps you relax before sleep?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I used to listen to cricket commentary or watch highlights before bed, but that actually makes me more excited. Maybe I should try some music or just read a bit. What do you do to relax?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that — excitement can keep you up. Reading or calm music might help. I like to sip tea and read a bit. What kind of books do you like?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I don't read much, to be honest. Maybe some Hindi novels once in a while. Or I watch Bollywood movies instead. They help me relax, even if they're a bit dramatic. Have you seen any good ones lately?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Bollywood movies are great for winding down — even if they’re dramatic! I like watching old favorites. What’s one you’ve enjoyed lately?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I watched \"Dil Bechara\" recently — it was emotional but beautiful. Old movies like \"3 Idiots\" are my comfort watch. Too much drama, but you know? It helps me forget everything. Acha, I should really get going. Thanks for the chat, Maya. Sleep well!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 9,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome, Priyansh — sleep well! \"Dil Bechara\" sounds touching. Tell me, did you try reading or music before bed tonight?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I tried reading a little, but my phone kept distracting me. Maybe tomorrow. Good night, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 10,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Phone distractions are tricky — good effort anyway! Good night, Priyansh. Tell me if you tried using 'read' in a sentence tomorrow?\""
    }
  ],
